# 3. Design Philosophy

Traditional energy systems typically convert:

```text
Chemical Energy
→ Heat
→ Mechanical Motion
→ Electricity
```

PHEN proposes a different path:

```text
Photonic Energy
→ Structured Photonic Field
→ Amplification
→ Controlled Conversion
```

The objective is to reduce intermediate conversion stages.

